title: War of the Roses: They've Only Gone On a Couple Dates
description: Lily went to a concert with a guy she was seeing but while at the concert they ran into a girl he knew and she felt like he was totally flirting with her.  Now Lily wants to know if he's seeing someone else or what the deal was with that situation.
